{{ToolIcon|polygon}}

With this tool you can draw polygons. Click the {{MouseButton|left}} to indicate the starting point and successive vertices, then double-click or press &lt;kbd>Enter&lt;/kbd> to connect the last vertex to the starting point.

&lt;kbd>shift&lt;/kbd>+{{MouseButton|left}} undoes the last clicked point.

